{"abstract":[{"text":"iOS delivers an incredible collection of graphics, media, and integrated technologies for developing cutting-edge mobile games. Explore the frameworks and technologies that enable you to create the most imaginative games possible. Dive into expert techniques to harness the full capabilities of iOS and create rich gameplay experiences for your players. This is the first of two sessions covering the techniques for iOS game development.","type":"text"}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes","doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes\/WWDC11"]]},"sections":[],"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/wwdcnotes\/wwdc11-402-essential-game-technologies-for-ios-pt-1"]}],"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"patch":0,"minor":3},"metadata":{"title":"Essential Game Technologies for iOS, Pt 1","modules":[{"name":"WWDC Notes"}],"roleHeading":"WWDC11","role":"sampleCode"},"kind":"article","identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes\/WWDC11-402-Essential-Game-Technologies-for-iOS-Pt-1","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"content","content":[{"level":2,"text":"Overview","type":"heading","anchor":"overview"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"😱 “No Overview Available!”","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Be the hero to change that by watching the video or reading the transcript on WWDCIndex and providing notes! It’s super easy:"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"https:\/\/wwdcnotes.com\/documentation\/wwdcnotes\/contributing","isActive":true}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"sampleCodeDownload":{"action":{"type":"reference","identifier":"https:\/\/nonstrict.eu\/wwdcindex\/wwdc2011\/402\/","isActive":true,"overridingTitle":"Open on WWDCIndex"},"kind":"sampleDownload"},"references":{"https://nonstrict.eu/wwdcindex/wwdc2011/402/":{"identifier":"https:\/\/nonstrict.eu\/wwdcindex\/wwdc2011\/402\/","check